{"tid":320882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【ATM人扮？】銀行換鎖工人被困提款機 收據口遞紙仔求救","createTime":"2017-07-14T00:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T00:30:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9bd0a4dbb87ccf0369e17d0f8dcce2caa01e78","tid":320882,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:16:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>【ATM人扮？】銀行換鎖工人被困提款機 收據口遞紙仔求救</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時國際  2017-07-14 07:12:02 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n工人被困珀斯克里斯蒂市這間美國銀行分行的ATM內，只好遞紙條向顧客求救。(互聯網)<br />\n「提款機是人扮的」這個笑話已經講了很久，但美國德州這部提款機內真的有人。一名外判工人在換鎖時被困在提款機房內，他卻沒有帶手機，只好從提款機收據口遞紙條出去，跟顧客求救。<br />\n<br />\n事發於科珀斯克里斯蒂市（Corpus Christi）一間美國銀行（Bank of America）分行。顧客收到的其中一張紙條寫道，「請救我。我被困在此。我沒有帶手機。請打給我老闆」，然後附上了一個電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n有些顧客以為這是個惡作劇，幸好有人打電話報警，警員到場踢開門才救他出來，當時他已經被困兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n去救人的警員奧爾登（Richard Olden）也忍不住笑說：「我們聽到機器裏面傳出一點小聲音。你人生再也不會見到這樣的事了，某個人被困在ATM機內。太瘋狂了。」<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司"},{"pid":"0a00808e6f087d8914c65841fded5d078dd27dc5","tid":320882,"uid":60190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e8547501cb869363f5dab21f48a13556a737bc","tid":320882,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66aaef387a87ef0d791a55d739e65b240e990d1","tid":320882,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:22:07.000Z","msg":"都話真"},{"pid":"ff32df52156ce88aea55278f3f440f466c98e6c5","tid":320882,"uid":67719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c540c096c40234abfac4c53b101416447ae16f","tid":320882,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7f36bed99cde5dec13ee9678f3568c4d374336","tid":320882,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/083025_dbef5cbcb3fc2aac358d1d1b903df3d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F083025_dbef5cbcb3fc2aac358d1d1b903df3d8.jpg&h=74c6302f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}